---
title: Teriyaki Beef & Veggie Bowl with Garlic Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: Make a simple stir-fry a little more special by serving with mouth-watering garlic rice! Plus, using our delicious teriyaki sauce
means you get a big helping of flavour with minimal effort. Enjoy your tasty and colourful creation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-beef-veggie-bowl-2f3171ad.jpg
